data.description: Welcome to this stunning East Cobb home nestled in the coveted neighborhood of Kings Farm, renowned for its exceptional location within the Pope High School district. This beautiful residence boasts a timeless aesthetic with its white-painted 3-sides brick exterior, situated on a full-finished terrace level.    Comprising 5 bedrooms and 5 bathrooms, this home features an open concept design, highlighted by an updated white kitchen that brings an air of modern elegance to the space. Natural light floods the interior, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere throughout.     The expansive owner's suite provides a sanctuary with a sitting room, dual owner's closets, and an owner's bath featuring dual sinks and a linen closet nestled between them. Additionally, this remarkable residence boasts ensuite secondary bedrooms, with one fully renovated to elevate convenience and privacy to new heights.    The terrace level of the home is dedicated to entertainment, featuring a media room complete with a bar, ideal for hosting gatherings or enjoying movie nights with loved ones. Recent upgrades include a new HVAC system and carpeting, ensuring comfort and style throughout the home. Step outside to discover a vast, level flat backyard, offering ample space for outdoor activities and entertaining.    Additionally, the property boasts updated exterior paint and light fixtures, welcoming guests with its enhanced curb appeal. Professionally landscaped grounds showcase low-maintenance yet stunning floral arrangements, trees, and perennials, inviting residents to embrace the best of life amidst the beauty of nature.     With numerous updates and meticulous attention to detail, this East Cobb gem offers a harmonious blend of luxury, comfort, and functionality, creating the perfect backdrop for modern living.
